{"tid":19052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Miss著超短裙起哄動 直播上課86萬人觀看","createTime":"2016-12-02T15:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-08T04:48:27.000Z","uid":294,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31557fb2cdc3ce6551c55b771c557ed034c38b39","tid":19052,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/aries8248/videos/722888791208980/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Faries8248%2Fvideos%2F722888791208980%2F&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGonvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=3b9a32c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/aries8248/videos/722888791208980/</a> <br />\n<br />\n38min 直播 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.azureedge.net/newsimages/2016/12/01/729671-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.azureedge.net%2Fnewsimages%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F729671-XXL.jpg&h=f8c3d967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣一間高中近日有代課女教師，穿着性感「超短裙」教英文，該出位教師更將上課情況透過社交網站直播，引起哄動，吸引高達86萬人觀看。 <br />\n<br />\n網名「艾瑞絲」的台灣網紅昨日到當地大同高中，以代課身份試教一節英文課，她當日穿着超短裙上課，露出一雙美腿，配合熱褲和黑絲襪，展現美好身段，性感誘人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pics.ctitv.com/wpimg/2016/12/7.jpg  \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpics.ctitv.com%2Fwpimg%2F2016%2F12%2F7.jpg%20%20&h=925a2111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n艾瑞絲在社交網站貼文解釋：「其實我沒有真的要當老師，我大學選修了教材教法課，教授要我們去高中部試教很高興有這個經驗，雖然我語無倫次，手抖個不停，但很謝謝班上同學們的包容，大家都超可愛的，年輕真好啊～」 <br />\n<br />\n對於引起哄動，她亦表示驚奇：「平常直播遊戲都才一兩百人看而已⋯⋯怎麼直播試教，突然衝到兩三千人在看，嚇我一跳。」 <br />\n<br />\n網友對艾瑞絲性感上課意見紛紜，有人讚她：「如果我以前我有這種老師，我一定不會蹺課。」但也有人批評她：「這樣稱得上是教學嗎？有足夠的專業知識？適合做為人師？不是誤人子弟？教學計畫紀錄清楚教學方式和目標？如何設計活動測試教學成效？ 妳還是不要浪費自己的時間才能，當英文老師是不會讓妳成名和致富！」 <br />\n<br />\n艾瑞絲是台灣知名電玩女郎，曾獲得「電玩女神」季軍，以一雙纖細的美腿出名。"},{"pid":"93da65da1d95de6e9d1b20f70d3cd8f59f8221b8","tid":19052,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3101ec47ab8d1c5d4b950b9a23a442b6d7d6e22a","tid":19052,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:16:19.000Z","msg":"過膝長襪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deee7fefb65818b62c0a9da3aec40df143673ac5","tid":19052,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"又可以收貴d<br />\n<br />\n幾識marketing<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\n等緊比盡巴打入來quote"},{"pid":"2a723f47cdc45ac23b456d992aff9a84da05ce87","tid":19052,"uid":4168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"佢教邊科先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c26aafbbd52e8dcd605d587260ea518c7d7aab7","tid":19052,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"麻麻"},{"pid":"8139e7f3629394b8613f15f662e712544d7de126","tid":19052,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"覺下面班友會打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f312bcd5f615ac015d2d0007a3c2e5821581e3","tid":19052,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢教邊科先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c76d26c2814b806563e1672f4f392e2c665dc8d","tid":19052,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺下面班友會打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9747ea17ebe86c066aac4f75c78c3b112d27ff14","tid":19052,"uid":6347,